description: Cheesed and Confused is grilling up an old fashioned comfort food with a gourmet twist to go along with their "fancy soups." Their grilled sandwiches are filled with a number of tasty meats and veggies like bbq pulled pork, bacon and gorgonzola, prime rib beef and onion, and much more. Make sure to get a tomato parmesan soup, or some tater tots to complete your meal.
name: Cheesed and Confused
